Did you give him a chance? Did you?

508
00:48:07.739 --> 00:48:09.240
Answer me!

509
00:48:12.726 --> 00:48:14.061
Stop that guy!

510
00:48:19.032 --> 00:48:20.278
Thanks.

511
00:48:31.119 --> 00:48:32.184
See you.

512
00:48:53.887 --> 00:48:57.283
Freeze! We've got the place
completely surrounded.

513
00:49:39.897 --> 00:49:42.133
Oh. no. My God.

514
00:49:44.443 --> 00:49:47.523
Oh. no. Oh. my God. No!

515
